data.description: FIND YOUR LAKE WISCONSIN BREEZE ON LAKEVIEW AVE UP THE STREET FROM THE ICONIC MERRIMAC FERRY!  THIS OPEN CONCEPT RANCH HAS AN EXPANSIVE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH EN SUITE FEATURING DUAL SINK VANITY, DREAM SHOWER AND ENORMOUS WALK-IN CLOSET.  FULLY  UPDATED KITCHEN (2018) OPENS TO DINING AND LIVING ROOM WITH VAULTED CEILING AND GAS FIREPLACE.  DEDICATED BATH FOR BED 2 AND BED 3, FINISHED BASEMENT WITH BAR AREA AND WORK OUT ROOM, A HUGE BACK DECK AND HEATED GARAGE; THIS PROPERTY HAS IT ALL.  THE COMMUNITY SHARES A PICNIC PAVILLION, SWINGS AND PLAYSET WITH SHARED GREEN SPACE ADJACENT TO THE SUBJECT PROPERTY.  IN ADDITION TO THE RECREATION OFFERED BY THE LAKE, YOU ARE SURROUNDED BY HIKING, BIKING, SKIING AND ALL MANNER OR DINING, ENTERTAINMENT AND RETAIL.  DON'T JUST LIVE SOMEWHERE, LOVE SOMEWHERE!
